* * * * * * * *
* Candl 0.4.0 *
* * * * * * * *

Install
-------

To install candl, PIPLib must be installed. Optionally, scoplib must
be installed to enable SCoP support.

$> ./configure --with-piplib=/path/to/piplib/install --with-scoplib=/path/to/scoplib/install

$> make

$> make install


